nd some times insulating. In 1973 he was awarded the <a href=\"http:\/\/en.wikipedia.org\/wiki\/A._A._Griffith_Medal_and_Prize\" title=\"A. A. Griffith Medal and Prize\">A. A. Griffith Medal and Prize<\/a>.<\/p>","name":"Nevill Francis Mott","place_of_birth":"Leeds ,  England","place_of_death":"Milton Keynes ,  Buckinghamshire ,  England","text":"Nevill Francis Mott , Physics, 1977","year":1977.0}